Chordate:



Chordate sighed happily. Once more, Feline was holding onto his arm.  She 
kissed him on the cheek, Chordate smiling, the leopard-bot resting her head 
on his shoulder as they walked towards a randomly picked room.

"You're welcome." he said, hoping it would take a long time to get to her new 
quarters.
